Action should return a list of consequences for given formats/scenarios
Action should perform its consequences on a given controller as a given format
ActionTemplate should provide an interface to find templates by name
ActionTemplate should have a block to prepare an action
ActionTemplate should yield a new action to its block
ActionTemplate should build an action using its block and a list of formats
Adherence should provide a DSL for creating/registering action templates
Consequence should run symbol args as methods
